r.'=>'<br>* 非活动语言对管理员来说仍然可见且处于活动状态。对于其他用户，它们不会在语言切换器中显示，也无法访问。','Active*'=>'激活','Optimize Database'=>'优化数据库','Cleans up all trp_original_strings table of duplicate rows. This table contains strings in the default language, without any translation.<br>The trp_original_meta table, which contains meta information that refers to the post parent’s id, is also regenerated.<br>Such duplicates can appear in exceptional situations of unexpected behavior.'=>'清理表trp_original_strings所有重复行。此表包含默认语言的字符串，没有任何翻译。<br>trp_original_meta表（其中包含引用帖子父级 id 的元信息）也会重新生成。<br>在出现意外行为的特殊情况下，可能会出现此类重复项。','Remove duplicate rows for original dictionary strings'=>'删除原始字典字符串的重复行','Cleans up all trp_dictionary_* tables of duplicate rows. These tables contain translations for user-inputted strings such as post content, post title, menus etc.'=>'清理所有trp_dictionary_* 表中的重复行。这些表包含用户输入字符串的翻译，例如帖子内容、帖子标题、菜单等。','Remove duplicate rows for dictionary strings'=>'删除字典字符串的重复行','Cleans up all trp_gettext_* tables of duplicate rows. These tables contain translations for themes and plugin strings.'=>'清理所有trp_gettext_* 表中的重复行。这些表包含主题和插件字符串的翻译。','Remove duplicate rows for gettext strings'=>'删除 gettext 字符串的重复行','Operations to perform'=>'要执行的操作','Select the languages you wish to make your website available in.<br>The Formality field is used by Automatic Translation to decide whether the translated text should lean towards formal or informal language. For now, it is supported only for a few languages and only by <a href="%s" target="_blank">DeepL</a>.'=>'选择您希望网站使用的语言。<br>自动翻译使用 "正式性 "字段来决定翻译文本应偏向正式还是非正式语言。目前，它仅支持少数语言，且仅由<a href="%s" target="_blank">DeepL</a> 支持。','Informal'=>'样式1','Formal'=>'正式','Default'=>'默认','Formality'=>'礼节','Removing untranslated dictionary strings where translation is available for language %s...'=>'删除未翻译的字典字符串，其中翻译可用于语言%s...','Removing duplicated dictionary strings for language %s...'=>'正在删除语言%s的重复字典字符串...','Removing untranslated gettext strings where translation is available for language %s...'=