 include translated links in sitemaps generated by SEO plugins.<br/>Requires <a href="https://translatepress.com/docs/addons/seo-pack/" title="TranslatePress Add-on SEO Pack documentation" target="_blank"> SEO Pack Add-on</a> to be installed and activated.'=>'不要在SEO插件生成的站点地图中包含翻译的链接。<br/>需要安装和激活<a href="https://translatepress.com/docs/addons/seo-pack/" title="TranslatePress Add-on SEO Pack documentation" target="_blank">SEO Pack Add-on</a>。','Exclude translated links from sitemap'=>'从站点地图中排除已翻译的链接','If your problem still isn\'t solved, try asking your hosting about your errors. The most common issue is missing permissions for the SQL user, such as the Create Tables permission.'=>'如果问题仍未解决，请就此错误咨询您的主机服务商。最常见的问题是 SQL 用户缺少权限，例如"创建表"权限。','Plan C.'=>'计划 C.','Test it to see if everything is working. If something went wrong, you can restore the backup that you\'ve made at the first step. Check if no more errors occur while browsing your website in a translated language. Look at the timestamps of the errors to make sure you are not seeing the old errors. Only the most recent 5 errors are displayed.'=>'测试一下，看看是否一切都在工作。如果出现问题，您可以恢复第一步所做的备份。在以翻译的语言浏览您的网站时，检查是否不再出现任何错误。查看错误的时间戳，以确保您没有看到旧错误。仅显示最近的 5 个错误。','Copy the relevant content from the duplicated tables (trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es_COPY for example) in the newly generated table (trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es) -- perform this step only if you want to keep the current translations'=>'从新生成的表 （trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es_COPY） 中的重复表（例如trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es_COPY）中复制相关 trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es内容 -- 仅当您想要保留当前翻译时，才执行此步骤','Go to Settings -> TranslatePress -> General tab and Save Settings. This will regenerate the tables using your current SQL server.'=>'转到设置->翻译->常规选项卡中并保存设置，此操作将在您的 SQL 服务器上重新生成数据表。','Remove the trouble tables by executing the DROP function on them'=>'通过执行故障表上的 DROP 函数来删除它们','Create a copy of each translation table where you encounter errors. You can copy the table within the same database (trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es_COPY for example) -- perform this step only if you want to keep the current translations'=>'在遇到错误时创建每个翻译表的副本。您可以在同一数据库中复制该表（例如，trp_dictionary_en_us_es_es_COPY）-仅在想要保留当前翻译的情况下执行此步骤','Create a backup of your database'=>'创建数据库备份','If your problem isn\'t solved, try the following steps:'=>'如果您的问题没有解决，请尝试以下步骤：','Plan B.'=>'计划 B.','Go to Settings -> TranslatePress -> General tab and Save Settings. This will regenerate the tables using your current SQL settings. Check if no more errors occur while browsing your website in a translated language. Look at the timestamps of the errors to make sure you are not seeing the old errors. Only the most recent 5 errors are displayed.'=>'转到设置->翻译->常规选项卡中并保存设置，此操作将使用当前 SQL 设置重新生成表。使用已翻译的语言浏览网站，检查错误是否不再发生，查看错误的时间戳，以确保您没有看到旧错误，仅显示最新的 5 个错误。','Plan A.'=>'计划 A.','What you can do in this situation'=>'在这种情况下您可以做些什么','The SQL errors detected can occur for various reasons including missing tables, missing permissions for the SQL user to create tables or perform other operations, problems after site migration or changes to SQL server configuration.'=>'检测到的 SQL 错误可能出于各种原因发生，包括缺少表、SQL 用户缺少创建表或执行其他操作的权限、此问题一般出现在站点迁移后或更改 SQL 服务器配置后。','If TranslatePress detects something wrong when executing queries on your database, it may disable the Automatic Translation feature in order to avoid any extra charging by Google/DeepL. Automatic Translation needs to be manually turned on, after you solve the issues.'=>'如果TranslatePress在数据库上执行查询时检测到错误，可能会禁用"自动翻译"功能，以避免 Google/DeepL 的任何额外费用。解决问题后，需要手动打开自动翻译。','Why are these errors occuring'=>'为什么会发生这些错误','These are the most recent 5 errors logged by TranslatePress:'=>'以下是TranslatePress记录的最新 5 个错误：','Logged errors'=>'记录的错误','Updating original string ids for language %s...'=>'正在更新语言%s的原始字符串 id ...','Cleaning original strings table for language %s...'=>'为语言%s清理原始元数据表…','Inserting original strings for language %s...'=>'插入语言%s的原始字符串…','The content of this element should be written in the default language.'=>'此元素的内容应以默认语言编写。','This element will still be visible when you are translating your website through the Translation Editor.'=>'当您通过翻译编辑器翻译网站时，此元素仍将可见。','Choose from which languages to exclude this element.'=>'从中选择要排除此元素的语言。','Select languages'=>'选择语言','Exclude this element from specific languages.'=>'从特定语言中排除此元素。','Exclude element from language'=>'从语言中排除元素','Choose in which language to show this element.'=>'选择显示此元素的语言。','Select language'=>'选择语言','Show this element only in one language.'=>'仅在一种语言中显示此元素。','Restrict element to language'=>'将元素限制为语言','Exclude from Language'=>'从语言中排除','Restrict by Language'=>'按语言限制','Please note that DeepL API usage is paid separately. See <a href="https://www.deepl.com/pro.html#developer">DeepL pricing information</a>.'=>'请注意，DeepL API 的使用是需要单独付费的。请参阅 <a href="https://www.deepl.com/pro.html#developer">DeepL 定价信息</a>。','Enable or disable the automatic translation of the site. To minimize translation costs, each untranslated string is automatically translated only once, then stored in the database.'=>'启用或禁用站点自动翻译。为了最大限度地降低翻译成本，每个未翻译的字符串仅自动翻译一次，然后存储在数据库中。','There are no logged errors.'=>'没有记录的错误。','TranslatePress Errors'=>'TranslatePress错误','Automatic translation has been disabled.'=>'自动翻译已禁用。','<strong>TranslatePress</strong> encountered SQL errors. <a href="%s" title="View TranslatePress SQL Errors">Check out the errors</a>.'=>'<strong>TranslatePress</strong>遇到 SQL 错误。<a href="%s" title="View TranslatePress SQL Errors">查看错误</a>。','Enables the hreflang="x-default" for an entire language. See documentation for more details.'=>'启用所有语言的 hreflang="x-default"。有关详细信息，请参阅文档。','Enable the hreflang x-default tag for language:'=>'为语言启用 hreflang x-default 标记：','Use this HTTP Referrer if the API lets you restrict key usage from its Dashboard.'=>'如果API允许您在其仪表板中的限制密钥使用，请使用此 HTTP Referrer。','API Key from settings page:'=>'来自设置页面的 API 密钥：','Only enable for testing purposes. Can impact performance.<br>All records are stored in the wp_trp_machine_translation_log database table. Use a plugin like <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-data-access/" target="_blank">WP Data Access</a> to browse the logs or directly from your database manager (PHPMyAdmin, etc.)'=>'仅为测试目的启用。<br>所有记录都存储在 wp_trp_machine_translation_log 数据库表中。使用<a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-data-access/" target="_blank">WP Data Access</a>等插件或直接从数据库管理员（PHPMyAdmin 等）浏览日志。','Add a limit to the number of automatically translated characters so you can better budget your project.'=>'对自动翻译的字符数添加限制，以便更好地为项目编制预算。','Block Crawlers'=>'阻止爬虫','Click here to check if the selected translation engine is configured correctly.'=>'单击此处检查所选翻译引擎配置是否正确。','Test API credentials'=>'测试 API 凭据','By upgrading you\'ll get access to all paid add-ons, premium support and help fund the future development of TranslatePress.'=>'通过升级，您可以访问所有付费附加组件、高级支持，并帮助为TranslatePress的未来发展提供资金。','Choose which engine you want to use in order to automatically translate your website.'=>'选择要使用的引擎，以便自动翻译您的网站。','Translation Engine'=>'翻译引擎','Enable Automatic Translation'=>'启用自动翻译','TranslatePress Automatic Translation'=>'TranslatePress自动翻译','Automatically translate your website through the DeepL API.'=>'通过DeepL API自动翻译您的网站。','The daily quota for machine translation characters exceeded. Please check the <strong>TranslatePress -> <a href="%s">Automatic Translation</a></strong> page for more information.'=>'超过机器翻译字符的每日配额。有关详细信息， <strong>请查看翻译 <a href="%s">>-自动</a></strong> 翻译页面。','Something went wrong, please try again.'=>'出错了，请重试。','DeepL'=>'DeepL','Automatic Translation'=>'自动翻译','Do not automatically translate these strings (ex. names, technical words...)<br>Paragraphs containing these strings will still be translated except for the specified part.'=>'不要自动翻译这些字符串（例如名称、技术词...）<br>包含这些字符串的段落仍将翻译，但指定的部分除外。','Exclude strings from automatic translation'=>'从自动转换中排除字符串','String'=>'字符串','Log machine translation queries.'=>'记录机器翻译查询。','Today\'s character count:'=>'今天翻译的字符数：','Limit machine translation / characters per day